1. *Nevolji* stvara odlučnost u čoveku. (Difficulties create determination in a person.)

2. *Nevolje* nam nisu nikakva prepreka. (Difficulties are no obstacle to us.)

3. *Nevoljnost* je karakteristika koja se ističe. (Unwillingness is a characteristic that stands out.)

4. Ima ljudi koji se ne osećaju *nevoljno* da se upuste u nove stvari. (There are people who are unwilling to embark on new things.)

5. Ponekad je *nevolja* samo u našim glavama. (Sometimes the difficulty is only in our heads.)

6. Usponi se pamte, a *nevolje* se zaboravljaju. (Ascents are remembered, and difficulties are forgotten.)